text: The Noakhali-11 was one of the electoral districts of the National Parliament of Bangladesh. It was a seat at the National Assembly located in Noakhali district. == History == Noakhali-11 was formed in 1973 but was discontinued in 1984. == Elected Members of Paraliment == Year of election Member of Party Party 1973 A. K. M. Shahjahan Kamal Bangladesh Awami League 1979 Mohammad Ismail Bangladesh Nationalist Party Term ended == References == Category:1984 disestablishments
